headline: Morgan Stanley names 3 highest conviction ideas in retail for 2026
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley has identified its top retail ideas for 2026, highlighting a divided landscape marked by scarce organic growth and the increasing importance of scale.

headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of AutoZone (AZO)
summary: Over the past six months, AutoZone’s stock price fell to $3,470. Shareholders have lost 6.1% of their capital, which is disappointing considering the S&P 500 has climbed by 11.5%. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
